('MyMemo AI', 'mymemo-ai', 'Transform digital chaos into an organized, AI-enhanced knowledge oasis.', 'In the digital age, we''re bombarded with information from every angle. It''s easy to feel overwhelmed by the sheer volume of digital content we encounter daily. Enter MyMemo AI, a cutting-edge tool designed to act as your personal "Digital Brain." This AI-powered platform specializes in organizing, analyzing, and retrieving your digital knowledge with ease and efficiency. From articles and videos to links and screenshots, MyMemo AI ensures that every piece of digital content is just a query away from being found. It''s like having a supercharged, AI-assisted memory at your fingertips, ready to simplify the chaos of our digital lives.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/cf7d237d19fb3ef443e067dacab504748c1f08bb-2492x1223.png', 'https://www.mymemo.ai/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}, {"plan": "Pro Tier", "price": "$7.99 per month", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Personalized AI Knowledge Database","Reflective Learning with AI Recaps","Multi-Language Support","Efficient Information Retrieval","Enhanced Knowledge Management"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
