('ChatPlayground AI', 'chatplayground-ai', 'Multi-chatbot powerhouse for AI tasks.', 'ChatPlayground AI revolutionizes the way users interact with multiple AI chatbots, offering a suite of 14+ powerful AI tools in a single subscription. Designed for developers, data scientists, content creators, students, and AI enthusiasts, it simplifies the process of accessing and utilizing various AI models, enhancing productivity and creativity.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/4b1b076f8133858a6784484ed3645293e6dcec2b-2497x1225.png', 'https://www.chatplayground.ai/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}, {"plan": "Pro Tier", "price": "$19 per month", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Multiple Chatbots Integration","User-Friendly Interface","Advanced Analytics","Cost Efficiency","Time Efficiency","Versatility"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
