('Scribble Diffusion', 'scribble-diffusion', 'Turn doodles into digital masterpieces with AI-powered Scribble Diffusion.', 'Scribble Diffusion is an innovative AI tool designed to transform sketches into polished images with the help of advanced artificial intelligence. This open-source project, brought to life by Replicate, is a testament to the marvels of modern technology, offering a bridge between raw creativity and digital artistry. Designed for artists, designers, and anyone in between, Scribble Diffusion simplifies the process of turning a simple doodle into a refined masterpiece.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/57aa0791daafd3cf27d092c263100c6cfc8e44a2-1408x868.jpg', 'https://scribblediffusion.com/', 'free', '[{"plan": "Customization and Flexibility", "price": "Custom", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"AI-Powered Image Generation","User-Friendly Interface","Open-Source Project","High Customization","Enhances Creativity","Time-Saving"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
('Andi', 'andi', 'Andi is a generative AI-powered search engine that provides direct answers instead of just links.', 'Andi represents a leap forward in search technology, harnessing the capabilities of generative artificial intelligence to transform how we find information online. Unlike traditional search engines that return a list of links, Andi provides direct answers to queries, akin to conversing with a knowledgeable companion. It''s tailored for users who value immediacy and precision in their information gathering process.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/6732f8ece2335beca9e6862c60b3a12abbccd06d-1680x876.png', 'https://andisearch.com/', 'free', '[{"plan": "Free Access", "price": "Free", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Generative AI Technology","Conversational Interface","Direct Answer Retrieval","Modern Browser Compatibility","Enhanced Search Efficiency","User-Centric Design"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
