('GPT for Sheets and Docs', 'gpt-for-sheets-and-docs', 'Elevate productivity in Sheets and Docs with AI-powered automation and creativity.', 'GPT for Sheets and Docs is an innovative AI tool designed to seamlessly integrate the capabilities of generative AI models directly into Google Sheets™ and Docs™. As someone who has reviewed numerous AI tools, I found this one particularly intriguing for its promise of bringing the full power of AI, including ChatGPT and other models like GPT-3.5, GPT-4 Turbo, and Claude AI, into the familiar interfaces of Google''s most popular productivity apps. This tool caters to both individual users and professionals seeking to enhance their productivity in data handling, content creation, and more, by automating tasks such as data cleaning, classification, extraction, translation, editing, and summarization directly within Sheets and Docs.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/99d9e73533dbb8b0058672873e016d1bd06ff799-1890x930.jpg', 'https://workspace.google.com/marketplace/app/gpt_for_sheets/677318054654', 'free', '[{"plan": "Free Tier", "price": "Free", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Bulk Processing Capabilities","Diverse Model Selection","Versatile Use Cases","Ease of Integration","Enhanced Productivity","Cost-Effective Solution"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
